**EVERY Sentry MCP tool call MUST include these parameters:**
- `organizationSlug`: "YOUR_ORG_SLUG"
- `projectSlugOrId`: "YOUR_PROJECT_SLUG"
- `regionUrl`: "https://YOUR_SENTRY_HOST"

